The original uploader has left this torrent for dead. Very annoying
I have found most of the files but the Bard, Prequel and his DH Special don't match any I know about.
As such I have seeded it to the extent I can but I don't think it will ever complete (95.1%) unless someone has the missing blocks.
You might want to look at my versions instead as that is where this poster got most of these files.
You can do that by clicking on my nic in this post.
